  "texts": [
    "Likewise, these tools should not be permitted in qualifying examinations that measure candidates' aptitude and eligibility to advance to higher stages of education.",
    "The use of ChatGPT has already been regulated in some educational institutions (Kalhan 2023).",
    "• Allow some generative tools to assist classroom-related writing, but this must be clearly credited by the author (Roe et al. 2023).",
